
# Master Node Components
1) Etcd (key-value store) database for k8s cluster, Provide high avalibility, Alway keep the backup for it (If master goes then we can restore with it)
2) Kube-api-server # API server is the entry point for all the REST commands used to control the cluster.
3) kube-controller # Manage bunch of job, Example automated task
4) kube-scheduler # Used to regulates task on work node

# Worker Node Components
1) kube-proxy
2) pods
3) kubelet